<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1830,2035]" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">
<bibRefCitation author="Toll, S." box="[151,350,1830,1855]" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" pagination="403 - 413" refId="ref7298" refString="Toll, S. (1936) Untersuchung der Genitalien bei Pyrausta purpuralis L. und P. ostrinalis Hb. nebst Beschreibung 11 neuer Microlepidopteren-Arten. Annales musei zoologici polonici, 11 (24), 403 - 413." type="journal article" year="1936">Toll (1936: 405)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Toll" authorityYear="1936" box="[486,644,1830,1854]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marginella">
<emphasis box="[486,644,1830,1854]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">S. marginella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[728,832,1830,1855]" country="Ukraine" name="Ternopil'" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">Ternopil‘</collectingRegion>
region of 
<collectingCountry box="[971,1061,1830,1855]" name="Ukraine" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
(”Podolien, Kreis Zaleszczyki, Wołczków“). This taxon was mentioned in various checklists as a species of uncertain taxonomic position (e.g., Elsner 
<emphasis box="[235,289,1902,1926]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">et al</emphasis>
. 1999: 50, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ponomarenko, M. G." box="[431,659,1902,1927]" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" pagination="87 - 106" refId="ref7066" refString="Ponomarenko, M. G. (2008) Gelechiidae. In: Sinev, S. Yu. (Ed.), Katalog Cheshuekrylykh (Lepidoptera) Rossii (Catalogue of the Lepidoptera of Russia). KMK Scientific Press, St. Petersburg-Moscow, pp. 87 - 106 + 327 - 329. [in Russian, English abstract]" type="book chapter" year="2008">Ponomarenko 2008</bibRefCitation>
: 101). An accurate drawing of the adult and male genitalia of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Toll" authorityYear="1936" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marginella">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">S. marginella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the original description agrees in all details with typical specimens of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityYear="1854" box="[1170,1375,1939,1963]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="consanguinella">
<emphasis box="[1170,1375,1939,1963]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">S. consanguinella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and therefore we synonymize 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Toll" authorityYear="1936" box="[441,591,1974,1998]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marginella">
<emphasis box="[441,591,1974,1998]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">S. marginella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityYear="1854" box="[654,853,1974,1998]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="consanguinella">
<emphasis box="[654,853,1974,1998]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">S. consanguinella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="353" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1830,2035]" lastBlockId="5.[151,1436,151,248]" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="353" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">
The name „ 
<taxonomicName authority="Herrich-Schaffer, 1854" authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityYear="1854" box="[340,894,2010,2035]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cassignatella">
<emphasis box="[340,616,2011,2035]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">Sophronia cassignatella</emphasis>
Herrich-Schäffer, 1854
</taxonomicName>
“ was mistakenly applied to a specimen of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityYear="1854" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="353" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="352" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="consanguinella">
<emphasis italics="true" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="353" pageId="4" pageNumber="352">S. consanguinella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Minusinsk, Krasnoyarskiy krai of 
<collectingCountry box="[774,849,151,176]" name="Russia" pageId="5" pageNumber="353">Russia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Bidzilya, A. V." box="[863,1069,151,176]" pageId="5" pageNumber="353" pagination="64 - 72" refId="ref6200" refString="Bidzilya, A. V. (2002) On the distribution of Gelechiid moths (Lepidoptera, Gelechiidae) in the Southern Siberia. Information I. The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette, 9 (1 - 2), 64 - 72." type="journal article" year="2002">Bidzilya 2002: 79</bibRefCitation>
). This mistake was duplicated in the catalogue of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="" authorityYear="1758" box="[352,487,188,213]" class="Insecta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="353" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Lepidoptera</taxonomicName>
of 
<collectingCountry box="[535,610,188,213]" name="Russia" pageId="5" pageNumber="353">Russia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Ponomarenko, M. G." box="[629,920,188,213]" pageId="5" pageNumber="353" pagination="87 - 106" refId="ref7066" refString="Ponomarenko, M. G. (2008) Gelechiidae. In: Sinev, S. Yu. (Ed.), Katalog Cheshuekrylykh (Lepidoptera) Rossii (Catalogue of the Lepidoptera of Russia). KMK Scientific Press, St. Petersburg-Moscow, pp. 87 - 106 + 327 - 329. [in Russian, English abstract]" type="book chapter" year="2008">Ponomarenko 2008: 101</bibRefCitation>
). The name 
<emphasis box="[1074,1380,188,212]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="353">
” 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityYear="1854" box="[1081,1373,188,212]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="353" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cassignatella">Sophronia cassignatella</taxonomicName>
“
</emphasis>
is a misspelling of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityYear="1854" box="[358,652,224,248]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" genus="Sophronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="353" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="consanguinella">
<emphasis box="[358,652,224,248]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="353">Sophronia consanguinella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and must be removed from the list of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stainton" authorityYear="1854" box="[1081,1215,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Gelechiidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="353" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Gelechiidae</taxonomicName>
of 
<collectingCountry box="[1252,1331,223,248]" name="Russia" pageId="5" pageNumber="353">Russia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
